1. CREATE

Use a POST method for creating a Person
localhost:8080/persons/
    {
        "name": "Cristian",
        "lastName": "Rincon",
        "age": 22,
        "address": "Fontibronx"
    }

Create Multiple Persons

localhost:8080/persons/

[
    {
        "name": "Cristian",
        "lastName": "Rincon",
        "age": 22,
        "address": "Fontibronx"
    },
    {
        "name": "David",
        "lastName": "Cadena",
        "age": 28,
        "address": "Calle 26 Cerca GE"
    }
]

2. READ

Use a GET method for obtain the information of the persons

localhost:8080/persons/

for individual person

localhost:8080/persons/{PersonId to get}


3. UPDATE

Use a PUT method for update

localhost:8080/persons/{PersonId to Update}


    {
        "name": "David",
        "lastName": "Guerrero",
        "age": 32,
        "address": "Calle 26 Cerca GE"
    }
    
    
4. DELETE

Use a DELETE method for delete a Person

localhost:8080/persons/{PersonId to delete}

